@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Draft : approve
Pending : entry / log depot
Draft --> Reviewed : cancel
Draft : entry / log depot
Reviewed --> Archived : approve
Archived --> Cancelled : submit
Cancelled --> OnHold : confirm
Archived --> Draft : revert
OnHold --> [*]
@enduml